", "@value": "Transportation Security Acquisition Reform Act", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": " a strategic multiyear technology acquisition plan,\n\t\t\t\twhich may include a classified addendum to report sensitive transportation\n\t\t\t\tsecurity risks, technology vulnerabilities, or other sensitive security\n\t\t\t\tinformation; and", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Congress", "@entity-id": "0001"}], "#text": "not later than 180 days after the date of\n\t\t\t\tenactment of the ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(1)"}, "@id": "H4CAAD6762C4D4CBC80B02EDBA192A660", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "to the extent\n\t\t\t\tpossible, shall publish such plan in an unclassified format within the public\n\t\t\t\tdomain."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(2)"}, "@id": "H3656BA0A6C104844A3F0E6681C6F54B0", "#text": "\n                    "}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "H1EF4926271B3495BB275F27985761631"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " shall develop the multiyear acquisition plan in consultation with\n\t\t\t\tthe ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": ", the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Under Secretary for Management", "@entity-id": "7050"}, {"#tail": ", and the\n\t\t\t\t", "@entity-parent-id": "7000", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Chief Information Officer", "@value": "Chief Information Officer"}, {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Under Secretary for Science and Technology", "@entity-id": "7040"}], "#text": "The\n\t\t\t\t"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "Consultation"}, "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "HBC6B0341D6B648939842FB8376C382F2"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The multiyear acquisition plan shall include the\n\t\t\t\tfollowing:"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(c)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "Contents of\n\t\t\t\tplan"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "section 707", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:707"}, "#text": "An analysis of transportation security\n\t\t\t\trisks and the associated technology gaps, including consideration of the most\n\t\t\t\trecent Quadrennial Homeland Security Review under ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(1)"}, "@id": "H4095623D78474D0DB5D4037D3A46DE5B", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "A set of\n\t\t\t\ttransportation security-related technology acquisition needs that\u2014"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(2)"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "H280CF62640A8466BA2A6048FF61C4AE1", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": "; and", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (1)", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:1611/ss:c/p:1", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "is prioritized\n\t\t\t\tbased on risk and gaps identified under "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "H6856E5BE87C74C44ABCFDE40F88ACC8A", "#text": "\n                      "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "includes\n\t\t\t\ttechnology acquisition roadmaps with defined objectives, goals, and\n\t\t\t\tmeasures."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "HADCC403045AB4E3B888413D1F7B4930A", "#text": "\n                      "}]}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "An identification\n\t\t\t\tof test, evaluation, modeling, and simulation capabilities that will be\n\t\t\t\trequired to support the acquisition of the security-related technologies to\n\t\t\t\tmeet those needs."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(3)"}, "@id": "H89BF211EEA77427EA22839DABAE63EBB", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "An identification\n\t\t\t\tof opportunities for public-private partnerships, small and disadvantaged\n\t\t\t\tcompany participation, intragovernment collaboration, university centers of\n\t\t\t\texcellence, and national laboratory technology transfer."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(4)"}, "@id": "H70D09A94D7D940BEB44B7E96E1EC5C3A", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " acquisition workforce needs that will be required for\n\t\t\t\tthe management of planned security-related technology acquisitions, including\n\t\t\t\tconsideration of leveraging acquisition expertise of other Federal\n\t\t\t\tagencies.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administration\u2019s", "@entity-id": "7013"}, "#text": "An identification\n\t\t\t\tof the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(5)"}, "@id": "HE382EFA8B9F746F1AAFC57CD5B5A9233", "#text": "\n                    "}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "HC32F38E358EC4D51B1ED8DC5A6088B58"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "To the extent\n\t\t\t\tpossible, and in a manner that is consistent with fair and equitable practices,\n\t\t\t\tthe plan shall\u2014", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(d)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "Leveraging the\n\t\t\t\tprivate sector"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "leverage emerging technology trends and\n\t\t\t\tresearch and development investment trends within the public and private\n\t\t\t\tsectors; and", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(1)"}, "@id": "H0D596CF82E614121B681BE6BBD8FF31E", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "incorporate feedback and input received\n\t\t\t\tfrom the private sector through requests for information, industry days, and\n\t\t\t\tother innovative means consistent with the Federal Acquisition\n\t\t\t\tRegulation.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(2)"}, "@id": "H68FF66653A0F40B692CA886E30F255B0", "#text": "\n                    "}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "HF8EF80C445A04DD38B4CA0236CF16AE3"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": " shall include with the plan required under this section a list of\n\t\t\t\tany nongovernment persons that contributed to the writing of the plan.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, "#text": "The\n\t\t\t\t"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(e)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "Disclosure"}, "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "H07B277FE61BF46D2A3762DBFFFBB962D"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " shall transmit to ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " an update of the plan.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Congress", "@entity-id": "0001"}], "#text": "Once\n\t\t\t\tevery 2 years after the initial strategic plan is transmitted to Congress, the\n\t\t\t\t"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(f)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "Update"}, "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "H69A2E87605D449B0A3F21F972AE28CEC"}], "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "HD509F610DC6B4C99BB8CF58BD49629C7"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "1612."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Acquisition\n\t\t\t\tjustification and reports"}, "subsection": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " implements any\n\t\t\t\tsecurity-related technology acquisition, the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administration", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " shall conduct a\n\t\t\t\tcomprehensive analysis to determine whether the acquisition is justified. The\n\t\t\t\tanalysis shall include, but may not be limited to, the following:", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}], "#text": "Before the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "Acquisition\n\t\t\t\tjustification"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "An identification\n\t\t\t\tof the type and level of risk to transportation security that would be\n\t\t\t\taddressed with the technology acquisition."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(1)"}, "@id": "H6E5C6AABBDC644A4AD6A5D45ABA7AD90", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "section 1611", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:1611", "@proposed": "true"}, "#text": "An assessment of how the proposed\n\t\t\t\tacquisition aligns to the multiyear plan developed under ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(2)"}, "@id": "HBF3997F0A0B1440AB8FEAD70E666171C", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "A comparison of\n\t\t\t\tthe total expected lifecycle cost against the total expected quantitative and\n\t\t\t\tqualitative benefits to transportation security."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(3)"}, "@id": "HCD62DA77C7A245948C9F1F88D15962B8", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "An analysis of\n\t\t\t\talternative security solutions to determine if the proposed technology\n\t\t\t\tacquisition is the most effective and cost-efficient solution based on\n\t\t\t\tcost-benefit considerations."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(4)"}, "@id": "H2777502BD5DE40D58C4C30DC7A5A5985", "#text": "\n                    "}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": ".", "@entity-parent-id": "7000", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Privacy\n\t\t\t\tOfficer of the Department", "@value": "Privacy Officer"}, "#text": "A determination\n\t\t\t\tthat the means of achieving such expected benefit to transportation security is\n\t\t\t\tconsistent with fair information practice principles issued by the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(5)"}, "@id": "H797EF62AB67C440B866DEB7D6F3CD424", "#text": "\n                    "}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "HE9A48C04A4704BD0B8D5A1E6F1DDE190"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Reports and\n\t\t\t\tcertification to congress"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " of a\n\t\t\t\tcontract for any security-related technology acquisition exceeding $30,000,000,\n\t\t\t\tthe ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administration", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " shall submit to the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " and the ", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Homeland Security of the\n\t\t\t\tHouse of Representatives", "@entity-id": "HHM00"}, {"#tail": " the results of the comprehensive acquisition\n\t\t\t\tanalysis required under this section and a certification by the ", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Commerce, Science, and\n\t\t\t\tTransportation of the Senate", "@entity-id": "SSCM00"}, {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\tthat the security benefits justify the contract cost.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}], "#text": "Not later than the\n\t\t\t\tend of the 30-day period preceding the award by the ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "H1CC523C93F7B4EF99FBCA400F7D436E1"}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " may reduce the\n\t\t\t\t30-day period under ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " to 5 days in order to rapidly respond.", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (1)", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:1612/ss:b/p:1", "@proposed": "true"}], "#text": "If there is a known or suspected\n\t\t\t\timminent threat to transportation security, the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "Extension due to\n\t\t\t\timminent terrorist threat"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "HA0EC4C7726C24A90B525BBC850E7DE82"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " shall provide immediate notice of such\n\t\t\t\timminent threat to the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " and the ", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Homeland Security of the House of\n\t\t\t\tRepresentatives", "@entity-id": "HHM00"}, {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation of\n\t\t\t\tthe Senate", "@entity-id": "SSCM00"}], "#text": "The "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(3)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "Notice to\n\t\t\t\tCongress"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "HE14E60DB252641BB8568B5979D86835F"}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "H626748FE36F54AECB7588BEA35D138C6"}], "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "H0E2C034F9C7F43BB8EE62F0C6BB06E62"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "1613."}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Acquisition\n\t\t\t\tbaseline establishment and reports"}, "subsection": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Baseline\n\t\t\t\trequirements"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " implements any security-related\n\t\t\t\ttechnology acquisition, the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administration", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " shall establish and document a set of\n\t\t\t\tformal baseline requirements.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}], "#text": "Before the "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "HB1E74353158A4448BF0BB4E85619AB0C"}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "@id": "HECBED262334B4355A82F490EBEBA3931", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "Contents"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The\n\t\t\t\tbaseline requirements shall\u2014"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "include the estimated costs (including\n\t\t\t\tlifecycle costs), schedule, and performance milestones for the planned duration\n\t\t\t\tof the acquisition; and", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@id": "H6B242FE11959460884E12E5D76B9F470", "#text": "\n                      "}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "identify the\n\t\t\t\tacquisition risks and a plan for mitigating these risks."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@id": "H4D9316B1FD734E108DA57CB62C117F35", "#text": "\n                      "}]}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": ", the ", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (2)", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:1613/ss:a/p:2", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\tshall, to the extent possible and in consultation with the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": ", ensure that achieving these milestones is\n\t\t\t\ttechnologically feasible.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Under Secretary for\n\t\t\t\tScience and Technology", "@entity-id": "7040"}], "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\testablishing the performance milestones under "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(3)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "Feasibility"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "HD899E89ACB9045E5A8BAA27AFB78F147"}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": ", in consultation with the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": ", shall develop a plan for testing and\n\t\t\t\tevaluating the acquired technologies against the performance requirements\n\t\t\t\testablished under ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Under\n\t\t\t\tSecretary for Science and Technology", "@entity-id": "7040"}, {"#tail": ". The test and evaluation plan shall describe\n\t\t\t\tthe necessary and cost-effective combination of laboratory testing, field\n\t\t\t\ttesting, modeling, simulation, and supporting analysis to ensure that the\n\t\t\t\ttechnologies meet the ", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (2)", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:1613/ss:a/p:2", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": " mission needs.", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administration\u2019s", "@entity-id": "7013"}], "#text": "The "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(4)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "Test and\n\t\t\t\tevaluation plan"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "H9652FFB29511416DB7FA28B16C35F800"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " may utilize independent reviewers to\n\t\t\t\tverify and validate the performance milestones and cost estimates developed\n\t\t\t\tunder ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (2)", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:1613/ss:a/p:2", "@proposed": "true"}], "#text": "The "}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(5)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "Verification and\n\t\t\t\tvalidation"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "H2E6644A4F28C40A8945925C449A1FC2D"}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "HB3B9C9F293834945B71BAF7D09CE7236"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(b)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Review of\n\t\t\t\tbaseline requirements and deviation; report to Congress"}, "paragraph": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\tshall review and assess each implemented acquisition to determine if the\n\t\t\t\tacquisition is meeting the baseline requirements established under ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection\n\t\t\t\t(a)", "@value": "Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:1613/ss:a", "@proposed": "true"}], "#text": "The ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(A)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "#text": "\n                      ", "@id": "H87B8CC1F569F4D1ABB05FB96430607A4"}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The review shall include an assessment of\n\t\t\t\twhether the planned testing and evaluation activities have been completed and\n\t\t\t\tthe results of such testing and evaluation demonstrate that the performance\n\t\t\t\tmilestones are technologically feasible."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(B)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "Test and\n\t\t\t\tevaluation assessment"}, "#text": "\n                      ", "@id": "H64362571165044198B528310231D3E0F"}], "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "Review"}, "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "HF780E578118F4B65BF61C78F1FD91105"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                    ", "clause": [{"#tail": "\n                      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the actual or\n\t\t\t\tplanned costs exceed the baseline costs by more than 10 percent;"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                        ", "#text": "(i)"}, "@id": "H93C0D5B46810415EBFF804CBCEC0B91F", "#text": "\n                        "}, {"#tail": "\n                      ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "the actual or\n\t\t\t\tplanned schedule for delivery has been delayed by more than 180 days; or"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                        ", "#text": "(ii)"}, "@id": "H41A78716F8E6433B994B817DDBBE078F", "#text": "\n                        "}, {"#tail": "\n                    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "there is a\n\t\t\t\tfailure to meet any performance milestone that directly impacts security\n\t\t\t\teffectiveness."}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                        ", "#text": "(iii)"}, "@id": "H54BA990DF7604219857C0D8D20EE0D10", "#text": "\n                        "}], "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(A)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\tshall report to the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Administrator", "@entity-id": "7013"}, {"#tail": " and the ", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Homeland Security of the House of\n\t\t\t\tRepresentatives", "@entity-id": "HHM00"}, {"#tail": " the results of any assessment that finds that\u2014", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation of\n\t\t\t\tthe Senate", "@entity-id": "SSCM00"}], "#text": "The ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "#text": "\n                      ", "@id": "HBEEE029071C841C4A2C639C3D9A4E1EB"}, {"#tail": "\n                    ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "#text": "The report shall include the cause for such\n\t\t\t\texcessive costs, delay, or failure, and a plan for corrective action.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(B)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "Cause"}, "#text": "\n                      ", "@id": "H546C2865B87C40928FAA45B044450E11"}, {"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": " and the ", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Homeland Security of the House of\n\t\t\t\tRepresentatives", "@entity-id": "HHM00"}, {"#tail": " no later than 30 days after identifying such excessive costs, delay,\n\t\t\t\tor failure.", "@entity-type": "committee", "#text": "Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation of\n\t\t\t\tthe Senate", "@entity-id": "SSCM00"}], "#text": "The report required under this section\n\t\t\t\tshall be provided to the ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "(C)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                      ", "#text": "Timeliness"}, "#text": "\n                      ", "@id": "H771B268502B14AB7ADA2AA6E8F217A4B"}